        "x": 0,
        "y": 40
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Where these findings go & how to dig in\n\n- **Routing:** every rule here carries `domain=security` \u2192 Alertmanager route 5 \u2192 **ntfy `/security`** (digest) or **pages** when `severity=critical` (after 14-day soak).\n- **IDS drill-down:** [IDS Monitoring dashboard](/d/ids-monitoring) \u2014 Suricata signatures, Zeek conn/dns/http/ssl/ssh/files/notices.\n- **Host posture:** [Fleet](https://fleet.home.shdr.ch) \u2014 osquery policy pass/fail across 9 enrolled hosts.\n- **Alert rules & state:** [Grafana Alerting](/alerting/list?search=label:domain%3Dsecurity).\n- **Raw forensics (no alert):** Explore \u2192 ClickHouse (`zeek.*`, `suricata.*`) / Loki (tetragon, wazuh, keycloak).\n- **Soak \u2192 promote:** warning rules flip to `critical` after 14 clean days; suppress noisy Suricata SIDs in `rules.yml` (`alert_signature_id NOT IN (...)`)."
      }
    }
